'''ĶUDUTĻA MUSAL MUĦAMMAD (MUSALAV)'''
             (1651— 1716)
Muħammad havuna Ķudutļ rosuļ (hanjeseb Cħargabi sweruchļiyalda) miskinav maærulav mashurav âlimċi Musal chiżanalda. Hev, ķa'anatab beærab pahmuyaļul, berhun raq ðhodorav vas ðhalana zin jindirgo emen Musadasan, zingi Daghistanaļul biszungo ļiqal ustarżabażdai, xaduseb antļgo sonaļ ðalun vugo Makkæalda Yemenaldasa heniv csarav ðhar raærav âlimċi Saliħil madrasæalda.
Berharav âlimċigi vachun, Musalav vacsun vugo Daghistanalde va tholabgo ûmru hes tļun bugo maærulażda hortļob ļæ-êlmu thobithiżabiyaļe. Hes nache tarab beċedab êlmiyab irsalda hortļor rugo Ârabaļgi Avar maðhaļgi chwaral shi'yruyal asaral. Hev kkola Avarażul chwavulab adabiyataļe tļucs ļurav thozevesev ra'yul ustar. Musalav xun vugo, Makka-Madinæalde unago, Ħalabala-Aleppo shaharalda. Henib bugo hesul xobgi.
